37-b69b-54ccbe125502&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=The+Wall+Street+Journal&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAARKhfx291OmAYumsY52rVJK7Sq7aRY0fZURvmD2wGQ8i&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Finfinity-train-review-an-endless-ride-through-dreamlike-worlds-11564687906" class="rapid-with-clickid">绝对一流</a></ins><ins><a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:The Wall Street Journal;elmt:;cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=2f007401-3eaa-4237-b69b-54ccbe125502&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=The+Wall+Street+Journal&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAARKhfx291OmAYumsY52rVJK7Sq7aRY0fZURvmD2wGQ8i&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Finfinity-train-review-an-endless-ride-through-dreamlike-worlds-11564687906" class="rapid-with-clickid"><em>无限列车。</em></a></ins>丹尼斯在<em>《无限列车》</em>的所有四个赛季中担任剧集主管，之后你永远不会猜到，它被取消，然后被麦克斯彻底删除。没有官方 DVD 或蓝光光盘，但您可以通过亚马逊和苹果以数字方式购买剧集，看看有什么大惊小怪的。</p><p>与此同时，《 <em>Among Us》</em>系列还没有发布日期，尽管该剧由动画协会而非 WGA 负责报道，因此工作应该能够在不跨越纠察线的情况下进行。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/among-us-cartoon-coming-from-teams-behind-infinity-train-and-star-trek-lower-decks-184059395.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/among-us-cartoon-coming-from-teams-behind-infinity-train-and-star-trek-lower-decks-184059395.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> ffa3187e-445b-453e-a1ad-52f3f4fef8d8</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jun 2023 18:40:59 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687890547</ingested><modified> 2023-06-27T18:29:11+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Visual Arts]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Humanities]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]